      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "VP"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      06                   to   p-lnr                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A stampa fincatura                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     int-pag-sta-300.
       int-pag-sta-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
